node.text:
Watch how my facial hair has evolved over the years and how I use @braun_global’s new Series 7 both as a tool of self-expression and to manage my desired look on a daily basis! Well-groomed stubble or clean-shaven, whatever look you desire the Series 7 is here to help you #SayItWithAShave

Follow this link (https://bit.ly/3k22n28) to learn more about the Series 7 and comment below with the funniest moment of your shaving journey! Ad

#BraunUK #SayItWithAShave

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Marino Katsouris in London, United Kingdom with @legendlondonco. May be an image of 1 person, standing and outdoors.

node.text:
If anyone asks, this is how you hail a taxi in London

AD @legendlondonco jeans allowing me to perform the act with perfect form & manoeuverability - use support code: MARINO if you grab a pair

Hotel ARMS 💪🏼

Quick arm workout this morning to make wearing shirts even harder 👌🏼 Give it a go ⬇️

1. Seated Barbell curl into standing 6 reps each 3 sets
2. DB skull crushers (flick DBs away) 3x12
3. Hammer twist curls 3x10
4. Bench dips 3x20-25
5. Rope curl 3x12-15
6. Cable kick backs 3x12-15
(Superset each bicep exercise with a tricep)

Limited equipment in this one, but you don’t need much for a great arm pump 👊🏼

node.text:
High Volume CHEST & BACK 🙌🏼

I absolutely love pairing these two muscle groups together. Why? Well they are antagonistic muscle pairs, one contracts while the other one relaxes/stretches, resulting in a great pump 👌🏼

The workout (All supersets)
1. Chest fly’s into neutral pull down 4x10/12
2. Hex press into bent over row 4x8-10
3. Flat machine press into supinated pulldown 4x12-15
4. Bodyweight Dips into pull ups 4x failure
5. 10x 15m prowler push @vitorcarlosfit on top for extra resistance 😂

Full outfit from @rise - code: MARINO for a discount on everything on their site 👊🏼

node.text:
LEG DAY FINISHER 🔥

Refuelled with @myproteinus The Whey - use code: MARINOVIP

The workout:
1. Air bike legs only 30s
2. DB forward lunges 20 reps
3. Burpees 10 reps
4. Sissy squats 5 reps
Repeat 5 times with little to no rest 😅

This one honestly had me questioning why I do this to myself half way through. Give it a go for that extra burn at the end of your session!

AD #cardio #myprotein #legday

node.text:
Barn Door Back Workout 🛡

All the training volume is right here in this workout 😂 I definitely needed a rest day after this one.

The workout:
1. Deadlifts 5x10/10/8/6/4 into ⬇️ (excuse the face)
2. Pull ups 5xfailure
3. One arm rows 3x10 + dropset
4. Machine pull overs 4x12
5. Machine pull down 4x10
6. T bar rows 4x15/12/10/8 + dropset
7. Machine rear delt fly 4x15-20

Training vest from @rise - code: MARINO

Pulling 5 plates for the first time in a while which felt good! Will aim to make this a comfortable working weight over the next few months 👌🏼
